{"tid":61712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2 0 1 6 大 美 人 李 嘉 欣 大 事 回 顧！","createTime":"2016-12-31T12:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T01:07:16.000Z","uid":53178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4c7383270ea7009c8b7015df8562770e47c248","tid":61712,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"2016即將完結，我大美人李嘉欣決定同大家回顧大美人16年5件大事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一位：<br />\n美人委屈滯新千歲機場</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n北海道12月底的一場50年一遇大雪，癱瘓整個新千歲機場，亦令帶同仔仔小JM去旅行的許氏夫婦滯留機場多日。國泰航空安排混亂，令大美人險成難民，分別在Instagram和微博狠批航空公司安排奇差！此事被不少熱心巴絲瘋狂轉載，差點令全個LIHKG一致支持聲援大美人，希望她能早日回港。得到大量網民祝福和愛戴的大美人，最終不負眾望，成功返港！雖然滯留多日，大美人面露一絲疲倦，但美人保養有功，回港仍能保持最佳狀態，仍然是大家心目中最愛、最漂亮的大美人李嘉欣！而且北海道之旅的戰利品載滿兩車，完全稱得上是凱旋回歸，霸氣盡現！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恭喜恭喜！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb1vQuu7qhnQRzmpzTdEA4D922ATLXbuUv1FC9bhVFB7n?filename=s711fS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs711fS8.jpg&h=1edc66ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcVcDZ2DsXsyvRENdQCrNoE4jitJy6rxhqHDNXGKZnSs8?filename=3Tu10z8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Tu10z8.jpg&h=456169d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbckZm4XuE9ydmQdmZmpFpmKAzNDJPCZsBA7QpzCDFH1Y?filename=Rc5kc6i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRc5kc6i.jpg&h=77c2e0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第二位：<br />\n美人慘被梁唐青儀撞車尾</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今年4月，CY三女行李門事件引起多方討論，亦令到很多陳年資訊浮面，其中2004年有關梁唐青儀和大美人李嘉欣的新聞亦有出現。事源，梁唐青儀有一天駕駛7人車，在港島大坑道與大美人李嘉欣的平治座駕相撞。彭姓司機稱，當時「龍蝦」的七人車尾隨平治，並撞向車尾。但「龍蝦」當時話趕時間，相約司機第日再到現場商討賠償。司機之後向車房詢問，得知修理費需要萬幾蚊，告知梁唐青儀，但她不同意，結果傾唔埋欄唯有報警！<br />\n<br />\n報道引述梁太當時反斥彭姓司機也有責任，說「佢『屈』我！」而通常這種後車撞前車的意外，後車司機責任較大。事件係真係假無從稽考，但道理永遠都在大美人身上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/201846_ca07763bc6fa59a7f335eb0d3c4ae8f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F201846_ca07763bc6fa59a7f335eb0d3c4ae8f8.jpg&h=bf1377e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三位：<br />\n恭喜Post變被恭喜</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2016年2月8日，猴年大年初一，大美人李嘉欣有心地在Instagram上載一段「馬騮揈手揈腳」短片應節。短片背景配樂是普通話版的「恭喜恭喜恭喜你呀！恭喜恭喜恭喜你！」用意向各位網民拜年。豈料網民竟不斷留言：「我真係恭喜你呀」。其他網民亦笑指回應「有聲」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYJndDYeum1F1dw1VxFFu8P47JjUKGpAQSCjpCqA15vYC?filename=3Zf5444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Zf5444.jpg&h=3ccc444d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第四位：<br />\n大美人大方祝福甘比</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n富商劉鑾雄與甘比入紙結婚，舊愛大美人李嘉欣出席公益活動時大方地送上祝福，她說：「恭喜他。」被問到大劉病情好轉時，大美人更大方指健康開心最重要，人逢喜事就開心健康，會祝福他。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPogiiNgBN8TWH5T41GpH65WNDDma2ZMCpBeoabTWP9RB?filename=O478Z2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO478Z2C.jpg&h=7ea83e6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第五位：<br />\n大美人黎明世紀合照</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n4月下旬，黎明為慶祝入行30周年，在中環海濱長廊舉行一連8場戶外個唱，作為陳年緋聞女友的大美人李嘉欣，更跟丈夫許晉亨一起去捧場。事後她大方上載兩張合照至微博，留言：「感動的演唱會，加油!」，而在Instagram她就寫道：「Proud of your 香港精神 排除萬難」。不少網民都感到很驚訝，因為指嘉欣跟前任現任一起拍照；網民又指黎明跟嘉欣係是當年的金童玉女，而二人現時感情可見仍然友好，亦有網民稱讚「亨亨」夠大量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/31/201920_c97fbc4efa966a3f3764defccd1345cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F31%2F201920_c97fbc4efa966a3f3764defccd1345cd.jpg&h=b4d8528f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2016 將 成 過 去<br />\n2017 即 將 來 臨<br />\n大 美 人 誓 必 越 戰 越 勇！</span></span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXUcwAatnM94v3VZqMSbjwMGv61DZD4J33KznSNiC5LAA?filename=3298hZi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3298hZi.jpg&h=14ed1fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恭喜恭喜！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"398ec164f531485b2c7608433c34ba4e5c7d4db1","tid":61712,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我</span></span>"},{"pid":"201912ec6717108b3370ffdcd8554c500a08a043","tid":61712,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f5395524f92c2aef00f1b6fa45d698517552be21","tid":61712,"uid":6530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係</span></span>"},{"pid":"b4daa204e9e621637a74846d5ac467e42afa45a5","tid":61712,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:39:02.000Z","msg":"你唔滯留我落大雪嚟把撚呀 ?!"},{"pid":"e704a7f53171412680a034c684c89690d040fae6","tid":61712,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一鍵留名"},{"pid":"f6eb6430f966d9e055352d182d6b92b68ce79d93","tid":61712,"uid":67917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9d811ef951964c36fb304d8d43d2565f5bcc763","tid":61712,"uid":69038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恭</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喜</span></span>"},{"pid":"40ea48d2451038007aa50e6cc956a1d65bed925b","tid":61712,"uid":46726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恭</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喜</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你</span></span>[/quote]"},{"pid":"8577d0fcf9fb7f81d8b2bd9baa1aeeda224a6886","tid":61712,"uid":40179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恭</span></span></blockquot